{
  "texts": [
    "• LaMini-LM (Wu et al, 2023).",
    "The LaMini-LM dataset is employed to train the LaMini model series.",
    "It comprises 2.58M English instructions, providing the advantages of a large scale and broad topic coverage.",
    "The creators utilize various instruction inputs from existing resources, including Self-Instruct, Flan 2022, and others, invoking the model to generate responses.",
    "The generation of instructions primarily follows guided strategies based on examples and themes."
  ]
}